        "### **Algorithms and Pseudocode**\n",
        "\n",
        "Before we write any code, we described the algorithm for each operation followed by pseudocode.\n",
        "\n",
        "<br>\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "### Algorithm 1: Add Flight (Sorted Insertion)\n",
        "\n",
        "**Goal:** Too insert a new flight into the roster so that the list remains sorted by departure time.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Steps:**\n",
        "1. We create a new flight node with the provided data.\n",
        "2. If the roster is empty, we set the new node as the head and return.\n",
        "3. If the new flight's departure time is earlier than the current head's departure time, we insert the new node before the head and update the head pointer.\n",
        "4. Otherwise, we set a pointer called `current` to the head and begin traversing.\n",
        "5. We advance `current` forward as long as the next node exists and its departure time is less than or equal to the new flight's departure time.\n",
        "6. Once we stop, we insert the new node between `current` and `current.next` by updating pointers.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Pseudocode:**\n",
        "```\n",
        "FUNCTION add_flight(flight_number, destination, departure_time, arrival_time):\n",
        "    new_node = FlightNode(flight_number, destination, departure_time, arrival_time)\n",
        "\n",
        "    IF head is None:\n",
        "        head = new_node\n",
        "        RETURN\n",
        "\n",
        "    IF new_node.departure_time < head.departure_time:\n",
        "        new_node.next = head\n",
        "        head = new_node\n",
        "        RETURN\n",
        "\n",
        "    current = head\n",
        "    WHILE current.next is not None AND current.next.departure_time <= new_node.departure_time:\n",
        "        current = current.next\n",
        "\n",
        "    new_node.next = current.next\n",
        "    current.next  = new_node\n",
        "END FUNCTION\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "<br><br>\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "### Algorithm 2: Cancel Flight\n",
        "\n",
        "**Goal:** To remove a flight from the roster using its flight number as the identifier.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Steps:**\n",
        "1. If the roster is empty, we print a message and return.\n",
        "2. If the head node matches the target flight number, we update the head to the next node.\n",
        "3. Otherwise, we traverse the list and check whether the next node is the one to remove.\n",
        "4. If we find it, we bypass it by linking `current.next` to `current.next.next`.\n",
        "5. If we reach the end without finding the flight, we print a not-found message.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Pseudocode:**\n",
        "```\n",
        "FUNCTION cancel_flight(flight_number):\n",
        "    IF head is None:\n",
        "        PRINT \"Roster is empty.\"\n",
        "        RETURN\n",
        "\n",
        "    IF head.flight_number == flight_number:\n",
        "        head = head.next\n",
        "        PRINT \"Flight cancelled successfully.\"\n",
        "        RETURN\n",
        "\n",
        "    current = head\n",
        "    WHILE current.next is not None:\n",
        "        IF current.next.flight_number == flight_number:\n",
        "            current.next = current.next.next\n",
        "            PRINT \"Flight cancelled successfully.\"\n",
        "            RETURN\n",
        "        current = current.next\n",
        "\n",
        "    PRINT \"Flight not found in roster.\"\n",
        "END FUNCTION\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "<br><br>\n",
        "\n",
        "### Algorithm 3: Validate Rest\n",
        "\n",
        "**Goal:** Traverse the roster and check that every pair of consecutive flights has at least a 12-hour gap (720 minutes) between the arrival of one flight and the departure of the next.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Steps:**\n",
        "1. If there are fewer than two flights, there are no consecutive pairs to check.\n",
        "2. We convert departure and arrival times from HHMM format to total minutes for comparison.\n",
        "3. We traverse the list. For each consecutive pair, we subtract the arrival time (in minutes) of the first flight from the departure time (in minutes) of the next.\n",
        "4. We handle the midnight crossing case by adding 1440 minutes when needed.\n",
        "5. If the gap is less than 720 minutes, we report a violation.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Pseudocode:**\n",
        "```\n",
        "FUNCTION validate_rest():\n",
        "    IF head is None OR head.next is None:\n",
        "        PRINT \"Not enough flights to validate.\"\n",
        "        RETURN\n",
        "\n",
        "    FUNCTION to_minutes(hhmm):\n",
        "        RETURN (hhmm // 100) * 60 + (hhmm % 100)\n",
        "\n",
        "    current   = head\n",
        "    all_valid = True\n",
        "\n",
        "    WHILE current.next is not None:\n",
        "        arrival_mins   = to_minutes(current.arrival_time)\n",
        "        departure_mins = to_minutes(current.next.departure_time)\n",
        "\n",
        "        IF departure_mins < arrival_mins:\n",
        "            departure_mins = departure_mins + 1440\n",
        "\n",
        "        gap = departure_mins - arrival_mins\n",
        "\n",
        "        IF gap < 720:\n",
        "            PRINT \"REST VIOLATION between [current] and [current.next]\"\n",
        "            all_valid = False\n",
        "\n",
        "        current = current.next\n",
        "\n",
        "    IF all_valid:\n",
        "        PRINT \"All rest gaps are valid.\"\n",
        "END FUNCTION\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "<br><br>\n",
        "\n",
        "### Algorithm 4: Display Roster\n",
        "\n",
        "**Goal:** Print all flights in the roster from head to tail in chronological order.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Pseudocode:**\n",
        "```\n",
        "FUNCTION display_roster():\n",
        "    IF head is None:\n",
        "        PRINT \"Roster is empty.\"\n",
        "        RETURN\n",
        "\n",
        "    current = head\n",
        "    WHILE current is not None:\n",
        "        PRINT current.flight_number, current.destination,\n",
        "              current.departure_time, current.arrival_time\n",
        "        current = current.next\n",
        "END FUNCTION\n",
        "```\n",
