        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## We choose Doubly Linked List as our Data Structure\n",
        "\n",
        "We choose a **Doubly Linked List** for the Global Fleet Database because it is the only structure from our allowed list that supports traversal in both directions:\n",
        "\n",
