        "\n",
        "### We also do not use a Stack or Queue\n",
        "\n",
        "This is because neither a **Stack** nor a **Queue** gives arbitrary access to internal elements. Both only expose one end for primary access. Performing a bidirectional search through the interior of these structures is not possible without destructively removing elements."
