        "2. At each node, we compare current.flight_id with the target flight ID.\n",
        "3. If they match, we add the delta value to current.assigned_crew. A positive delta increases the crew count and a negative delta decreases it.\n",
        "4. We print a confirmation message showing the updated values and return immediately.\n",
        "5. If the current node does not match, we advance current to the next node and repeat from step 2.\n",
        "6. If we reach the end of the list without finding a match, we print a message indicating the flight was not found.\n",
        "\n",
