        "# Section 8: Overall Complexity and Comparative Analysis\n",
        "\n",
        "## 8.1 Time Complexity Summary\n",
        "\n",
        "The table below summarizes the time complexity of every operation across all four phases.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Phase | Data Structure | Operation | Time Complexity |\n",
        "|---|---|---|---|\n",
        "| I | Singly Linked List | Add Flight (sorted insert) | O(n) |\n",
        "| I | Singly Linked List | Cancel Flight | O(n) |\n",
        "| I | Singly Linked List | Validate Rest | O(n) |\n",
        "| I | Singly Linked List | Display Roster | O(n) |\n",
        "| II | Doubly Linked List | Add Flight (append to tail) | O(1) |\n",
        "| II | Doubly Linked List | Update Staffing | O(n) |\n",
        "| II | Doubly Linked List | Bidirectional Search | O(n) worst, O(n/2) average |\n",
        "| II | Doubly Linked List | Display Fleet Status | O(n) |\n",
        "| III | Queue | Register Standby Crew | O(1) |\n",
        "| III | Queue | Retrieve Eligible Crew | O(n) |\n",
        "| III | Queue | Display Pool | O(n) |\n",
        "| IV | Queue | Enter Briefing Center | O(1) |\n",
        "| IV | Queue | Dispatch Crew | O(1) |\n",
        "| IV | Queue | Notify Captain | O(1) |\n",
        "| IV | Queue | Display Queue | O(n) |\n",
        "\n",
        "<br>\n",
        "\n",
        "## 8.2 Space Complexity Summary\n",
        "\n",
        "| Phase | Data Structure | Total Storage | Extra Memory Per Operation |\n",
        "|---|---|---|---|\n",
        "| I | Singly Linked List | O(n) — one node per flight | O(1) |\n",
        "| II | Doubly Linked List | O(n) — two pointers per node | O(1) |\n",
        "| III | Queue | O(n) — plus O(k) temporary during retrieval | O(k) where k ≤ n |\n",
        "| IV | Queue | O(n) — one node per crew member | O(1) |\n",
        "\n",
        "The doubly linked list in Phase II uses about twice as much pointer memory per node as the singly linked list in Phase I. Phase III is the only phase where an operation (retrieve_eligible) requires extra memory beyond O(1) during execution, due to the temporary holding queue.\n",
        "\n",
        "### 8.3 Insights\n",
        "**Most time-efficient phase:** Phase IV.  \n",
